The '''AQX aquatic explorer droid''' was a model of underwater explorer [[Droid/Legends|droid]]. AQX droids were used along with manned [[aquascout]]s by the [[Nexcore Mining Corporation]] to explore the depths of [[Velusia/Legends|Velusia]], looking for exploitable ore deposits.<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

